	importFolder: '/usr/share/tomcat/Voters/Georgia',
	zipName: "Georgia_Voters_Fixed.zip",
	compressedFile: 'DailyVoterBase_Fixed.txt'
]
def zipFile = new java.util.zip.ZipFile(new File(settings.importFolder,settings.zipName))

def voterEntry = zipFile.entries().findAll { !it.directory }.find { it.name == settings.compressedFile }
def modificationTime = (new Date(voterEntry.getTime())).format("yyyyMMdd")
println "${modificationTime} Mod Time"
println "Entry is ${voterEntry.name}"

def settings = [
	importFolder: '/usr/share/tomcat/Voters/Georgia',
	zipName: "Georgia_Voters_Fixed.zip",
	compressedFile: 'DailyVoterBase_Fixed.txt'
]
def zipFile = new java.util.zip.ZipFile(new File(settings.importFolder,settings.zipName))

def voterEntry = zipFile.entries().findAll { !it.directory }.find { it.name == settings.compressedFile }
def modificationTime = (new Date(voterEntry.getTime())).format("yyyyMMdd")
println "${modificationTime} Mod Time"
println "Entry is ${voterEntry.name}"

def unparsedTextFile = File.createTempFile('temp', '.txt')
unparsedTextFile.withWriter('unicode'){ w->
	def reader = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(zipFile.getInputStream(voterEntry), "UTF-8"))
	reader.eachLine { line -> 
		w<< line
	}
}
println "Temp file path: ${unparsedTextFile.canonicalPath}"
